These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, adventure, satire
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, cranberry, pepper
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, baccarat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, marigold
1. the person eating cranberry is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the person watching satire movies is the person eating pepper##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre      | satire  | time-travel       | adventure   |
| Food          | pepper | cauliflower | cranberry |
| Cigar         | tiparillo  | baccarat | pall-mall    |
| Flower   | marigold | zinnia       | lily      |

