.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, metal, trance
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, lavender
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, italian, turkish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, adventure, thriller
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the italian##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Music-Genre          | folk      | metal  | trance        |
| Color         | lavender | brown | blood-red |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian | turkish       |
| Movie-Genre           | thriller     | adventure     | animation      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, old-henry, swisher
House: cottage, futuristic, colonial
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, american, spanish
1. the swisher-smoker is the egyptian##1
2. the american is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the colonial house is in the middle##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | almond-milk        | mirinda |
| Cigar           | old-henry    | swisher | havana    |
| House   | cottage | colonial             | futuristic  |
| Nationality     | spanish     | egyptian                | american  |

