.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, ranch-style-climbing, skydiving
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, fonseca, swisher
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, western
House: townhouse, cottage, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is the ranch-style house##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby          | ranch-style-climbing    | skydiving  | baking      |
| Cigar           | swisher    | vegafina | fonseca |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | horror  | drama     |
| House   | townhouse | cottage    | ranch-style      |

