.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, boat, bike
City: prague, new-york, hamburg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, swimming
1. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the taxi##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking     | singing   |
| Transport           | bike       | boat   | taxi     |
| City   | new-york     | prague | hamburg |
| Sport           | swimming      | surfing         | climbing  |

