.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, polish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, water, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rat
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, teacher, project-manager
1. the polish is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
4. the colombian is on the left of the project-manager##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Nationality          | canadian | colombian       | polish |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | milk       | water   |
| Pet           | frog      | ferret       | rat     |
| Job         | fisherman   | teacher | project-manager  |

