.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
3 different games are played: poker, monopoly, domino
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, 7up
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, spy
3 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, ferret
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Game          | domino       | monopoly         | poker   |
| Beverage           | juice | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | mystery        | spy        |
| Pet   | hedgehog      | cat           | ferret        |

