.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, woodworking
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, cola
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, january, june
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, coral
1. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who likes blue is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| Beverage   | 7up | cola         | mirinda       |
| Birthday           | may      | june      | january         |
| Color     | blood-red      | coral         | blue          |

