.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, cycling, skateboarding
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, grey, black
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, sunflower
1. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who likes blue is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Sport       | cycling            | surfing      | skateboarding  |
| Color         | black | blue | grey |
| Pet         | goat               | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Flower   | zinnia             | sunflower       | poppy      |

