.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, electrician, scientist
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, snowboarding
House: palace, gothic-revival, cape-cod
City: hamburg, rome, edinburgh
1. the person who's sport is cricket is the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the electrician is on the far right##1
5. the chef is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | chef         | electrician |
| Sport   | skateboarding      | cricket | snowboarding     |
| House   | palace   | gothic-revival       | cape-cod     |
| City           | edinburgh    | rome         | hamburg        |

