2. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Job           | journalist | videographer | architect |
| Sport   | lacrosse        | cricket       | rowing     |
| Flower   | amaryllis     | tulip         | daisy     |
| Color     | lilac | purple          | azure      |

