.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, marigold
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, azure, chestnut
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
3 different games are played: snooker, canasta, go
1. the person playing go is the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | marigold    | bellflower | amaryllis |
| Color   | azure | brown     | chestnut     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | gospel        | folk        |
| Game           | canasta    | go         | snooker     |

