.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, writing
3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, domino
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, action, spy
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, november, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person playing bridge##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | cooking | writing   |
| Game           | domino     | canasta    | bridge   |
| Movie-Genre   | action         | spy    | fantasy   |
| Birthday         | november       | february | october |

