The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, biathlon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, bellflower, zinnia
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, motorbike
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the craftsman house is the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the tower house is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| House    | gothic-revival | craftsman     | tower      |
| Sport        | ice-hockey | skateboarding       | biathlon |
| Flower       | bellflower | azalea | zinnia  |
| Transport   | bus    | airplane   | motorbike  |

