There 3 different types of food: artichoke, kale, peas
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, ship, bus
House: wooden, art-deco, gothic-revival
1. the wooden house is on the far right##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the art-deco house is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
5. the nurse is in the middle##1
6. the person eating peas is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Job      | paramedic | nurse | scientist       |
| Food          | peas     | artichoke   | kale       |
| Transport         | car  | bus   | ship |
| House   | art-deco   | gothic-revival       | wooden  |

