The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, train
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growstulip is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
5. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |
| Birthday         | august     | january | may |
| City   | edinburgh  | london | hamburg       |
| Flower   | tulip    | iris       | amaryllis     |
