.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, rugby, weightlifting
House: townhouse, futuristic, tower
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, pony
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, punk
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the tower house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Sport      | weightlifting      | rugby    | surfing    |
| House          | tower         | futuristic    | townhouse   |
| Pet           | rabbit | pony | mouse |
| Music-Genre   | punk         | d&b     | folk    |

