There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, coral, red
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, jazz, rock
3 different games are played: scrabble, whist, domino
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who likes red##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Pet      | dog  | goldfish   | cat  |
| Color          | coral   | red | brown   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | disco      | rock    |
| Game   | whist | scrabble    | domino |

