.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, radish, zucchini
City: london, hamburg, paris
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, march, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person eating zucchini is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating radish##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Food      | radish         | zucchini     | lemon     |
| City           | hamburg        | paris | london |
| Birthday   | march        | april   | july    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby   | water-polo |

