.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, cat
City: prague, rome, marseilles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, r&b
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Pet          | cat     | goldfish    | mouse    |
| City         | prague | marseilles | rome     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | folk      | r&b        |
| Beverage         | water   | lemonade   | hot-chocolate |

 